{"tid":612811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【今日愚人節】David Webb爆獨家新聞！「港府下午發行基督債券」","createTime":"2018-04-01T06:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T00:52:11.000Z","uid":83582,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"304a9b99a717e7bd8474859fbd143c17d89cabc0","tid":612811,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T06:55:15.000Z","msg":"2018年04月01日<br />\n<br />\n 股壇長毛David Webb在復活節假期間，仍繼續發掘「獨家新聞」。在其網站披露港府因應多次發行伊斯蘭債券，仍未能成功將香港建成伊斯蘭金融中心，與此同時發現本港基督教氛圍原來較伊斯蘭教濃厚，故此下午宣佈發行基督債券（Christian Bond）。<br />\n<br />\nWebb引述消息指，基督債券將會於季度日（Quarter Days）派發利息，並且沒有指定贖回限期，不過當耶穌再次降臨世界時，持有者則可以贖回；或可以選擇在死前真誠地痛改前非，尋求贖罪，債券同樣可以贖回。<br />\n<br />\n至於應該向誰尋求贖罪？<span style=\"color: red;\">Webb指需要向選舉主任（Returning Officer）提出申請，選舉主任會視乎債券持有人是否真誠地願意悔改其罪行，以及過去是否有些行為反映該人並非真誠希望獲得贖罪。</span><br />\n<br />\n而過往未能避免利益衝突的行政長官及政務司司長，因為利益衝突而不能贖罪；<span style=\"color: red;\">一些聲稱因為受到神感召（called by god）而參選特首的行政長官，贖罪前需要提供通話紀錄或證據，證明神真的「call」了她，而並非妄想</span>，原因是「撻朵」違反選舉條例第27條。話雖如此，控罪亦須證明該名支持她參選的人是實際存在的。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，Webb的基督債券「獨家新聞」只是愚人節玩笑，讀者切勿認真，若想觀看全文，可到：<a href=\"https://webb-site.com/articles/christianbonds.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebb-site.com%2Farticles%2Fchristianbonds.asp&d=fO3Bk6jWbY6ghxLG0aYYBMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=3c8253bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://webb-site.com/articles/christianbonds.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n全球樓行 Dream House零距離<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&d=fO3Bk6jWbY6ghxLG0aYYBMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=ba398d96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Foverseasproperty&h=9bc132df\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/overseasproperty</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180401/58021232\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180401%2F58021232&d=fO3Bk6jWbY6ghxLG0aYYBMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=03e9b363\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180401%2F58021232&h=0b6113f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180401/58021232</a>"},{"pid":"fcd141a7ef603de6709ceb92f34f847053d7c48d","tid":612811,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T06:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8462da4192b52aa5c4b101c2c4ab29c5f5adb35","tid":612811,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T06:58:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88b3d9e9e71ece915ad7a9cd530385ed1ddeea0","tid":612811,"uid":39628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T07:00:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"661b7ac3a7fe333a1a22512168adc522aeecc4f6","tid":612811,"uid":19501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T07:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2eaa9e9b2c285d653de5a058569b0666b70202","tid":612811,"uid":34949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T07:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1610028b1d979dcde987dbb46b33be894a5ab55","tid":612811,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T07:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" cla